query:
SELECT ei.id, ei.employeeId, e.name as employee_name, ei.type, ei.amount, ei.invoiceDate, ei.reason, ei.branchId, b.name as branch_name
FROM employeeInvoices ei
JOIN employees e ON ei.employeeId = e.id
JOIN branches b ON ei.branchId = b.id
WHERE ei.type = 'negative';
